Invocation Name: still waters
des:
Get your morning off to a relaxed and focused start, or simply take a break in the middle of a hectic day to listen to the melody of still waters and birds chirping.
Featuring Psalm 23:2-3: "He makes me lie down in green pastures.
He leads me beside still waters. He restores my soul. He leads me in paths of righteousness."
